[AutoPilot R2 Left On/R2 Right off]
author=47iscool
description=Notes: Doesn't work right with the Porsche 911 GT3,
presumably because the car doesn't have any A.I. due to it
being hidden. Untested with the Diablo.

Also, if the code is disabled after the race finishes
you will be in control of the car instead of the A.I.
