[Create Porsche 911 (GT3) In Garage Slot 2]
author=InterAct
description=BACK UP your game save before using this code.</b>
This code will REPLACE any vehicle in garage slot 2.
When game is saved, any vehicle in slot two will become the Porsche.
If you can't get this to work:
1. Turn on codes.
2. Begin a new game and do not load your game save.
3. Go to the <b>Car Dealership</b> in <b>Simulation mode</b>.
4. Select <b>JPN</b>.
5. Select <b>Daihatsu.</b>
6. Purchase 2 <b>Mira TR-XX Avanzato R(J)</b>. (You'll need a vehicle in Garage Slot 2.)
7. Look in your garage for your new vehicle.
patch=1,EE,20959258,extended,6BF9FA35
