[Horsepower Boost Multiplier\HP Multiplier Slot01]
author=InterAct
description=<p>Replace ????? with one of the following values to multiply the stock Horse Power of the vehicle by the desired amount.</p> EXAMPLE:

Castrol Tom's SUPRA JGT(J)
Stock HP = 450HP
450 x 30.44 = 13698HP
New Horse Power of Castrol Tom's SUPRA JGT(J) would be roughly 13698 HP!

 HPx02.03 - 6E800
HPx04.06 - 6E0F3
HPx06.09 - 6D8E6
HPx08.12 - 6D039
HPx10.15 - 60834
HPx12.18 - 60027
HPx14.20 - 6F87A
HPx16.24 - 6F06D
HPx18.26 - 62868
HPx20.29 - 620BB
HPx30.44 - 639DD
HPx32.47 - 63158
HPx40.59 - 65169
HPx50.74 - 6AA18
HPx60.?? - 5B00C
patch=1,EE,D0C6B570,extended,1CD02FEB

