[License Codes\License B-1 Gold]
author=InterAct
description=<p>Turning on all of the Licence codes will NOT unlock vehicles.</p> License Cars can be unlocked if all of the License codes are on and you're able to get a gold in any of the tests.

EXAMPLE:

Activate all of the License B Gold codes and successfully complete License test B-1. If you complete test B-1 and receive a gold medal, you'll be awarded a bonus car.
patch=1,EE,20978430,extended,00000000

